all_answers.question: The ____ engine allows you to store, parse, and execute java applets, servlets, and stored procedures within the database
all_answers.subject: Business
all_answers.text: The JVM engine allows you to store, parse, and execute java applets, servlets, and stored procedures within the database. The JVM engine known has Java Virtual Engine is what allows a computer to run programs that use/need Java. Java is a plug-in that allows videos and other programs to run effortlessly on many devices.
